channel.title: Client error - Pictures & Video Provided :)
channel.description:
Ok, This Help thread I provide Pictures & Videos.
I'm using Palidino's client and get an error in the compiler and run.bat.
The Video includes another error the pictures don't have.
The error is "cannot find class."
Ive tried, changing the compiler paths and such and have pictures and videos to explain all.
In the past ive used this client and worked fine.
Past few days I redownload as I got back into 508's and get this error.
